  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">I camped him for literaly3 weeks.  One thing I noticed was he seems to have a trigger spawn.  It seems most people know to kill the undead, but every once in a while you will see a mummy called "a sand mummy".  If you kill this guy then within 1 minute the AC, or his place holder Sand Giant (much more common for the SG to spawn I'm afraid) will spawn somewhere in the zone.<br><br></td></tr>
