  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">Leodinus knows his stuff. I went to camp ac about 1/2 hour ago. It was about 8pm, so being a little late I ran to the tower and killed the spawn ("dry bone skeleton") I went to the large sand hill near the green to wait for 4am so I can start killing undead.. To my surprise at 3am the ancient cyclops spawned, within 10 minutes of getting there. By the way, I killed husam at about 7pm right when I zoned in. Spawning the Ancient Cyclops definitly has something to do with killing the tower spawn, probably at a certain time. Good luck with all your ring campin.<br>
