  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#13273C" class="c1">Followed Leodinus's advice:<br>
<br>
At 4am start killing undead on the desert side of SRO.    <br>
<br>
At roughly 6pm, kill the undead pop in the tower.    <br>
<br>
Hang out and wait for AC to pop...     <br>
<br>
This worked twice in 3 hours time over the weekend.<br>
<br>
It could be a coincidence, but this worked for us.    <br>
<br>
The real trick is to keep the other people from KS'ing your pop.  If you are fortunate enough to get him to spawn AND you are the first strike, people should respect this and watch the fun.  More likely, you'll have a much higher level player walk up, take him down and loot the ring with a smile on their face.<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
